question: Which of the following is not a property of Nylon-66?
option1: Nylon fibres have low tensile strength
option2: Nylon fibres are resistant to abrasion
option3: Nylon fibres are somewhat elastic in nature
answer: Nylon fibres have low tensile strength
explanation: Nylon fibres have high tensile strength. They are tough and resistant to abrasion. They are also somewhat elastic in nature.
